OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FTinder wants singletons to split with
OL,8,Fendless swiping as it bets on
OL,9,Fartificial intelligence (AI) to
OL,10,Fmatchmake Gen Z and crack app fatigue.
OL,12,FThe world's biggest dating app is
OL,13,Fhoping to reel younger daters back in
OL,14,Fafter rolling out a swathe of new
OL,15,Ffeatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
