PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774828709
OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FSeveral of these use AI to spot
OL,8,Fpersonality traits that it thinks will
OL,9,Flead to more tailored matches, while
OL,10,Fothers lean into a demand for real-
OL,11,Flife dating and student-focused
OL,12,Fmatching.
OL,14,FHillary Paine, Tinder's vice president
OL,15,Fof product management, said the app
OL,16,Fwas "invented for millennials" and
OL,17,Ftherefore "built for a generation that
OL,18,Fwas really geared towards convenience".
OL,26,@xD@EOUxD@^O]yD@KOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
