FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774828709
OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FBut she said Gen Z, which makes up
OL,8,Fabout 60% of its user base, wants
OL,9,Fdifferent things when it comes to
OL,10,Fdating.
OL,12,FShe told the Press Association: "We're
OL,13,Fhearing more and more from young
OL,14,Fdaters that app fatigue is real, not
OL,15,Fjust in the dating space but generally
OL,16,Fhow much time they're spending on
OL,17,Ftheir phones.
OL,26,@tD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
