PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774828709
OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,F"There's been this craving from
OL,8,Fyounger daters to get out into the
OL,9,Freal world and almost more
OL,10,Fserendipitously meet new people and
OL,11,Fstart dating.
OL,13,F"They're looking for authenticity and
OL,14,Fcompatibility rather than convenience
OL,15,Fand volume.
OL,17,F"A lot of the work that we're doing is
OL,18,Fin reaction to this new generation's
OL,19,Fways of dating."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@PO]
