OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774828709
OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FTinder, which launched in 2012, helped
OL,8,Fbring online dating into the
OL,9,Fmainstream and is now the world's most-
OL,10,Fused app with more than 630 million
OL,11,Fdownloads.
OL,13,FThe Los Angeles-based company is owned
OL,14,Fby Match Group, which owns a raft of
OL,15,Fdating platforms including Hinge and
OL,16,FOkCupid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
