PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774828709
OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FNew features for the app include an AI
OL,8,Ftool, which users can opt into, to
OL,9,Fscan the camera roll on people's
OL,10,Fphones and spot patterns such as
OL,11,Finterests, lifestyle and elements of
OL,12,Ftheir personality.
OL,14,FThis, along with asking the user
OL,15,Fspecific questions, means they can
OL,16,Freceive a daily curated recommendation
OL,17,Ffor a match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
