CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774828709
OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FOther new features include music and
OL,8,Fastrology "modes" to help people find
OL,9,Fmatches based on specific tastes `
OL,10,Fbuilding on the college or university
OL,11,Fmode for students to connect to others
OL,12,Fon their campus.
OL,14,FNearly 85% of users of its double date
OL,15,Ffeature, launched in the UK last
OL,16,Fsummer, are under 30, and it
OL,17,Fexperienced a surge in invites during
OL,18,Fpeak events such as Christmas and New
OL,19,FYear's Eve.
