OL,3,CTinder wants young singletons to break
OL,4,Cup with endless swiping amid new
OL,5,Cfeatures
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Tinder said it was piloting
OL,8,Fa new events feature in Los Angeles in
OL,9,Fa bid to tap into growing demand for
OL,10,Freal-life experiences, as well as a
OL,11,Fsoon-to-be-launched video speed dating
OL,12,Foption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
